": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/gate-enforcement.md\",\n          \"title\": \"GATE ENFORCEMENT - Edge Cases & Cross-Reference\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: GATE ENFORCEMENT - Edge Cases & Cross-Reference | Prioritize when: task context aligns with \\\"GATE ENFORCEMENT - Edge Cases & Cross-Reference\\\"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 11530,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/entity-cooccurrence-is-not-causal.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Entity Co-occurrence Is Not Causal Truth\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — only. They may improve search and ranking, but they must never be promoted as causal truth or overwrite a causal edge a… | Prioritize when: must write recall metadata only. Causal-edge writers may consume explicit causal declarations, lineage, or governed str…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 11529,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/deep-skill-workflow-required.md\",\n          \"title\": \"DEEP SKILLS — Use the Workflow, Never Hand-Roll\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Never Hand-Roll\\\" | Prioritize when: Never Hand-Roll\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"triggered\": [\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 1757,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/010-root-level-review-research-convention\",\n          \"tit