{"type":"text","timestamp":1781373047494,"sessionID":"ses_13de52a52ffewkjJmOhc1a75oH","part":{"id":"prt_ec21b9137001J7uD6NtUEU2MaN","messageID":"msg_ec21b6763001rd4iBqxe74KzLt","sessionID":"ses_13de52a52ffewkjJmOhc1a75oH","type":"text","text":"The deep-review skill requires command-owned state and forbids ad-hoc loop dispatch. I’m going to inspect the local workflow assets and reducer contracts, then write only the lineage artifacts under the override directory.","time":{"start":1781373047095,"end":1781373047491},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_070ba01715a27911016a2d987713c081919ca4f4ab6fd5fc19","phase":"commentary"}}}}
